(iii) The Insurance Regulatory and Development Authority of India
established under the Insurance Regulatory and Development Authority of
India Act, 1999;

(a) The process of appointment / reappointment of the IO/Dy. IO, adequacy of the
human resources and infrastructure provided to the office of the IO in relation to
the volume of complaints;

(b) Implementation of auto-escalation of the partially resolved or wholly rejected
complaints to the office of the IO within the timelines;
